The New Legends of Monkey - New episode: New Legends of Monkey

The Monkey King has returned... In new New Legends of Monkey, series two!

  • View comments 7

The Monkey King and his merry band of misfits must avoid demons, bandits and bounty hunters on their quest to find the sacred scrolls... Fortunately, the Monkey King has very (sometimes tiny) capable hands!

Don't miss a moment of the action, watch a new episode every Sunday on CBBC, with catch up available on iPlayer.

If you need more of a sneak peek, you can get a first look at the opening 2 minutes of the newest episode right now!
